icial day at my 9-5 was April 30th. After working there for almost 5 years, it was…","fields":{"date":"2021-06-03T06:28:35.614Z","slug":"/blog/my-first-month-as-a-freelancer/","collection":"blog","published":true,"externalLink":"","externalLinkLabel":"Check It Out »"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Quitting, Moving, & Getting Bit By A Dog","subtitle":"My First Month As A Freelancer","tags":["Freelance","Career"],"published":true,"featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/6b695/featuredImage.png","srcSet":"/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/2141d/featuredImage.png 132w,\n/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/7d3c7/featuredImage.png 263w,\n/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/6b695/featuredImage.png 526w,\n/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/c683a/featuredImage.png 1052w","sizes":"(min-width: 526px) 526px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/87113/featuredImage.webp 132w,\n/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/90103/featuredImage.webp 263w,\n/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/328c9/featuredImage.webp 526w,\n/static/b9f3f53624c7cc6f03898281feee4263/30766/featuredImage.webp 1052w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 526px) 526px, 100vw"}]},"width":526,"height":350}}}}},{"id":"4d2dfd53-353f-5200-9987-ee3cee0a2d32","excerpt":"So, you want to make some changes to an Open Source Repo? Good for you. That's the beauty of Open Source, even just fixing typos in the…","fields":{"date":"2019-11-02T17:12:33.962Z","slug":"/blog/sync-forked-repo/","collection":"blog","published":true,"externalLink":"","externalLinkLabel":"Check It Out »"},"frontmatter":{"title":"I've Forked The Repo, Now What?","subtitle":"Syncing Your Repo With the Upstream Repo","tags":["Git","Open Source"],"published":true,"featuredImage":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#080808","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/58ffde237fbc2fe080c4616ae4f133e5/8acf2/featuredImage.jpg","srcSet":"/static/58ffde237fbc2fe080c4616ae4f133e5/3ecf3/featuredImage.jpg 70w,\n/static/58ffde237fbc2fe080c4616ae4f133e5/8c6c6/featuredImage.jpg 140w,\n/static/58ffde237fbc2fe080c4616ae4f133e5/8acf2/featuredImage.jpg 280w,\n/static/58ffde237fbc2fe080c4616ae4f133e5/03484/featuredImage.jpg 560w","sizes":"(min-width: 280px) 280px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/58ffde237fbc2fe080c4616ae4f133e5/87492/featuredImage.webp 70w,\n/static/58ffde237fbc2fe080c4616ae4f133e5/e8d46/featuredImage.webp 140w,\n/static/58ffde237fbc2fe080c4616ae4f133e5/27a6a/featuredImage.webp 280w,\n/static/58ffde237fbc2fe080c4616ae4f133e5/56c16/featuredImage.webp 560w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 280px) 280px, 100vw"}]},"width":280,"height":350}}}}}]}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864","764694655"],"slicesMap":{}}